    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151220/extras/255428197a8886913e1dd37b307fd2bf.poster.avif?t=1769004987\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151220/extras/255428197a8886913e1dd37b307fd2bf.webm?t=1769004987\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151220/extras/255428197a8886913e1dd37b307fd2bf.mp4?t=1769004987\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You click, you dash, you slash.</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slice your way right into the action with simple controls. Your Dash is your attack: click the enemy, defeat the enemy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It doesn't stay that straightforward though: the enemies get trickier, their masses grow in number and your environment becomes more perilous. Easy to learn / harder to master. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151220/extras/aebcfab2c1dff878c3946cd14a4caadb.poster.avif?t=1769004987\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151220/extras/aebcfab2c1dff878c3946cd14a4caadb.webm?t=1769004987\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151220/extras/aebcfab2c1dff878c3946cd14a4caadb.mp4?t=1769004987\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Step into the One-Hit Hell.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every enemy is destroyed in one slash. But don't get ahead of yourself. You're a Glass Cannon: destructive but prone to shatter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this Instant-Death experience you should watch your step to not be caught easily. You fight alone / they are many.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151220/extras/3553799aa3fbc01ea71805ee607566d6.poster.avif?t=1769004987\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151220/extras/3553799aa3fbc01ea71805ee607566d6.webm?t=1769004987\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151220/extras/3553799aa3fbc01ea71805ee607566d6.mp4?t=1769004987\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Run it back.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Got knocked down? Get back up! Could you achieve a faster time? Make a run with as few dashes as possible? A combination of both? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep charging in and improve your times or try out the different ways to play Bot slash Bot. Prove yourself: you / the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151220/extras/ebe62b8d8806688a00daa71e5a4fd2aa.poster.avif?t=1769004987\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151220/extras/ebe62b8d8806688a00daa71e5a4fd2aa.webm?t=1769004987\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151220/extras/ebe62b8d8806688a00daa71e5a4fd2aa.mp4?t=1769004987\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You are free. The system keeping you in check has lost connection to your robot.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trapped in the maze-like guts of a colossal oil rig you quickly pick up your weapon and try to escape your corroding prison.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight with your dash. Slash your way through your former crew mates. It's all about speed / time is running out.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Slash your enemies with precision.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Danger Alert! The oil rig fights back with everything it has.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch out for machinery that has been converted into combat equipment and robot workers turning against you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The hot furnace spits its fire, oil streaks make you slip and the building is on the verge of collapse. Watch your every step / it could be your last.</p>",
